Hi there!

Unfortunately, this season's (season 7) ranked rewards end with "end of Season" - which was November 7th. However, the reset at the beginning of Season 8 (next season) isn't a hard reset. You'll be reset to a position relative to your current skill (your MMR). So while you can no longer earn Season 7 rewards, you can still work on your placements during pre-season (right now) for next season! Preseason games will have an impact on where you start for your placement matches next season!

Best of luck for Season 8! {{sticker:sg-kiko}}
